    {
      "id": "601913",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "fb_china_today",
        "uid": "8633"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t放开了中国人发现依然没有工作,经济崩溃<br/>\n连疫情的借口都没有<br/>\n<br/>\n共产党境遇更被动<br/>\n<br/>\n党国可以试试颠覆政权的准备好加速\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2022-11-28",
      "agree_count": 2,
      "discussion_count": 2,
      "discussions": [
        {
          "id": "1129208",
          "replier": {
            "username": "打土共分兰兰",
            "uid": "89718"
          },
          "date": "2022-11-28",
          "content": "不放开的话，没有工作的人依旧会造反，难道不是吗"
        },
        {
          "id": "1129219",
          "replier": {
            "username": "fb_china_today",
